{"tid":128724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(嗚啊)葉劉寸林鄭「只露三點」 稱拜票不能靠食殘廢餐","createTime":"2017-02-21T05:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T14:29:24.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e846f11eaa68d2e3c3b00de7d568649e5098642","tid":128724,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170221/large/1487649623_c354.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170221%2Flarge%2F1487649623_c354.jpg&h=1f1f99d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特首參選人葉劉淑儀今早接受電台訪問時，坦言現時選情很嚴峻，又透露有會計界好朋友選委告知她承受很大壓力，感到好可惜。她坦言，有意見指她與林鄭月娥的票源最相近，俱為女性及前政務官，且自己具有選舉經驗，「票源重疊，係嗰啲擅長選舉嘅人最怕，『集中票源，排除對手，高票當選，完成任務』，喺呢16個字目標下，咁咪排擠我」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170221/large/1487648494_ba76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170221%2Flarge%2F1487648494_ba76.jpg&h=3b06222f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對於有指林鄭月娥指若自己獲高提名票，是反映獲廣泛支持。葉劉揶揄她即使獲800票入閘，認受性都是低，且提名需開名，「好多人要畀面，暗票先係真正考量」。她又說：「佢(林鄭)話啲票自己嚟，呢句聽落幾好笑，梗係自己嚟啦，咁多人幫你拉，你自己心知肚明啦，講呢啲說話。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170221/large/1487645529_0788.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170221%2Flarge%2F1487645529_0788.jpg&h=dd48af04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她說建制及泛民的選委都有政治考慮，有人認為胡國興政綱較具吸引力，葉劉形容是「天馬行空」，年青人會很喜歡，又認為曾俊華入閘後可以鎅到林鄭月娥的票源，故送他入閘。她指送胡國興入閘，是因他可以隨意鬧，毋須收歛，亦有意識形態任何情況下，不會送某些候選人入閘。又透露早前兩次會見高教界選委，對方很客氣，但明言曾俊華及胡國興都有較多提名票，故會推二人入閘，而葉劉欠票太多，不會給票，葉劉說理解做法，但與他們能互相尊重，是很大得着。問到倘若輸掉選舉，有何感受，葉劉說「選舉唔係贏就輸，極少有人未有政綱就諗住贏，我無所謂」，又指自己選舉係為實踐政治理想及抱負，更了解社會，向市民介紹政綱，體現其政治理想，「我覺得我做到」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170220/large/1487577855_c6c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170220%2Flarge%2F1487577855_c6c6.jpg&h=37fe933c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n若最終不夠票入閘，會否將有關提名票給予其他參選人？葉劉指不會綑綁新民黨的票，但如果任何參選人要新民黨的票，都要到訪正式拜票，介紹政綱，爭取支持，回答問題，如自己在民建聯、工聯會、自由黨都未能獲票，但都曾多次拜訪，「公道吖，唔通個個都嚟食殘廢餐咩？我問你公唔公道先，你要親自嚟拜票，姓曾，姓胡，姓林嘅都要」。<span style=\"color: red;\">她又再不點名嘲林鄭「三點畢露」，「有參選人依家唔係『三點不露』，係只露三點(政綱)，係唔足夠架嘛，得三點之嘛，只露三點，你都要親自嚟同我地講，如果你要票，唔可以靠人哋嚟幫你打電話，咁嘅態度係唔啱」。</span>"},{"pid":"96d4fc428c9c014d4165923f375df45c7a9adb56","tid":128724,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:03:49.000Z","msg":"佢今次會唔會又唔夠提名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ee561ba9b3bb2a6ab8410815f78419b66a7317","tid":128724,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:05:34.000Z","msg":"比大陸玩咁多鑊都仲要幫住大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b4c23af64cbc14e662ba5a45e89acca0149f59","tid":128724,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:06:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢今次會唔會又唔夠提名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯定啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b5a64babc2d2e8bed74341409e85db500ffe73","tid":128724,"uid":47210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:07:34.000Z","msg":"佢真係輸到痴咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26147524f899202cfe93a7896a45f977830048c7","tid":128724,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:09:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢今次會唔會又唔夠提名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯定啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除左泛民票,基本佢同淋病都係靠建制票源,淋病一話選就已經𠝹走佢d票,好大機會又入唔到閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c42bba2a5ec496b97142c09ebc806697b10113","tid":128724,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:11:57.000Z","msg":"葉太咁鐘意講嘢語帶雙關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470dc7f2c6a36f0eac507210a5f4a2ea99fba551","tid":128724,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:16:43.000Z","msg":"又入唔到閘的話，我係葉劉既就即刻加入民主黨爭取真普選啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187c71101edce955a2441687776542c4d51aa246","tid":128724,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:24:06.000Z","msg":"葉太係咪忘記自己仲有兩個對手？係咁jer住個女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b38c12f0dd0e8211f543145fa9bba8e2a72a30c","tid":128724,"uid":7534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:28:26.000Z","msg":"酸到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  林奠係大仆街，呢個八婆都唔見得係好貨色，都係屎"},{"pid":"829d3379e06c1d664910fb06137ca8680532be09","tid":128724,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:35:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>葉太係咪忘記自己仲有兩個對手？係咁jer住個女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家都係女人同政務官背景<br />\n有比拼 競爭心理 就佢都講左<br />\n<br />\n最大問題 是 自己堆票源 <br />\n比林鄭借中共手夾走哂 <br />\n你係自己實力都算(某程度說服中共支持自己都係實力) 完全唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果2個 好老實  同佢無咩仇<br />\n由一開始 投果2個果堆 都無可能投佢"},{"pid":"ba0688b12df9818188cb1c866558598381d86126","tid":128724,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>葉太係咪忘記自己仲有兩個對手？係咁jer住個女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淋病目標係拎600甚至800提名票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309b5b8abb769f9ed95ba978f591c73c47472c26","tid":128724,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T08:19:44.000Z","msg":"放佢入去會有好多花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢講野大膽左好多"},{"pid":"60af9cc3d2b99f788a82e65d9130cf68814a0d12","tid":128724,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T13:21:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放佢入去會有好多花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢講野大膽左好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果佢真係入到閘, 就會馬上收皮,唔敢再9up嫁啦"},{"pid":"182ae1d1b02eeea011397ab220104f84eb3b47fe","tid":128724,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:29:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【邏輯推演】泛民選委應該同時提名胡國興葉劉淑儀</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/88966/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/88966/page/1</a></span>"}]}